name: CameraSky Australia
overview:
CameraSky is an online camera store in Australia. They deliver the wide selection of photographic equipment including digital cameras, DSLR, lenses and camcorders and accessories.

CameraSky delivers not only fun but also great value to photographers. The name “CameraSky” implicates that they share the same sky of cameras, photography and have specially created the store for your easier shopping.

All products are 100% genuine and brand new. They ship their products through their reputable international courier partners including FedEx, DHL, and UPS. Delivery is quick and as fast as within the next working day.
